column1: Define your casual wear collection with words that describe trendy and fashionable
column2: just include this remarkable invention by Span into it. The pair of red leggings is the ultimate partner for all those tunics that did not find a companion till now. You are sure to remain comfortable and at ease as this pair of tight fit leggings is crafted from 100 per cent cotton. The patch pockets at the back and the elastic waistband are the plus points of this Span creation.
